						"title": "Cloudflare named a strong performer in \"The Forrester Wave™: Serverless Development Platforms, Q2 2025\" report",
						"subtitle": null,
						"copy": "<div style=\"margin-top: 16px;\">\nWe are excited to announce that Cloudflare has been recognized as a Strong Performer in \"The Forrester Wave™: Serverless Development Platforms, Q2 2025\" report. \n</div>\n\n<div style=\"margin-top: 16px;\">\nWe believe this report validates Cloudflare's distinct approach to creating a scalable serverless development platform to build full-stack apps in any framework. Cloudflare's Workers, tightly integrated with Cloudflare's ecosystem and security, serves organizations with a developer friendly, zero downtime platform to build and integrate with no infrastructure to manage and complex configurations.\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"margin-top: 16px;\">\nAccording to the report, \"Cloudflare well suited for edge-first applications, APIs, and  performance-critical user facing services.\"\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"margin-top: 16px;\">\nCloudflare received the highest possible scores of 5.0/5.0 in 7 criteria:\n  <ul>\n    <li>Developer experience</li>\n    <li>Scaling</li>\n    <li>Cold start and latency optimization</li>\n    <li>Service level agreements</li>\n    <li>AI application development</li>\n    <li>Vision</li>\n    <li>Roadmap</li>\n  </ul>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"margin-top: 16px;\">\nRegister for the report to learn more.\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"margin-top: 24px;\">\n  <img src=\"https://cf-assets.www.cloudflare.com/slt3lc6tev37/588dgj5A36myDf8Ezs5Y6S/982a96059d31f6939c28083db78b7ecd/Image_Serverless-Development-Platforms-Q2-2025_1.png\" alt=\"Forrester wave serverless 2025\"/>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"margin-top: 16px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5; color: gray\">\nForrester does not endorse any company, product, brand, or service included in its research publications and does not advise any person to select the products or services of any company or brand based on the ratings included in such publications. Information is based on the best available resources. Opinions reflect judgment at the time and are subject to change. For more information, read about Forrester's objectivity <a href=\"https://www.forrester.com/about-us/objectivity/\" target=\"_blank\">here</a>.\n</div>",
